price: 133. Waxay (gaaladu) yidhaahdeen: Muxuu (Muxammad) noogu keeni waayey calaamo (mucjiso) xagga Rabbigii ah?” Miyaanay u imaan maraggii (ku sugnaa) Kutubtii hore (ee ku saabsanaa imaanshaha Nabiga).
arabic: وَقَالُواْ لَوۡلَا يَأۡتِينَا بِـَٔايَةٖ مِّن رَّبِّهِۦٓۚ أَوَلَمۡ تَأۡتِهِم بَيِّنَةُ مَا فِي ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur'an into the Somali language, translated by Abdullah Hasan Jacob.

meta.transliteration: waqālū lawlā yatīnā biāyatin min rabbihi awalam tatihim bayyinatu mā fī al-ṣuḥufi al-ūlā
